➜今日立冬时向寒
http://www.sohu.com/a/430327602_100281316	7021
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20201108/d3f7e4ae78624f5ca020ee90c4bb8455.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>今日立冬时向寒，人生花甲已觉晚。</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>万千心事撒星斗，留的悲伤透长天。</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20201108/45938ff335cf4cc29e678e665a145452.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>今日立冬时向寒，人生花甲尚未晚。</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>功名利禄桎梏尽，满目光华灿长天。</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20201108/063a0249f77b4cc293bca029503901b9.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
